API --> Application programming interface

REST API --> Representational State Transfer API
	Rules --> 
			1. Response should be same  irrespective of request platform
			2. Routes should be on the basis of nouns
				example --> /user, /auth, /plans
			3. HTTP methods should be used for doing operations on the Routes
			4. Data should be always in JSON format
			5. API should be stateless

	Why REST API -->
			1. 95% website use REST API
			2. Community support
			3. Standard way of writing APIs
			 